
User Guide
Upon opening the application, you will see a user interface with two dropdowns to select the base and target currencies, an input field to enter the amount, and a "Convert" button.

Select the base and target currencies from the dropdowns.

Enter the amount you want to convert in the input field.

Click the "Convert" button.

The application will fetch the latest exchange rates from the Free Currency API and display the exchange rate and the converted amount below the "Convert" button.

API
This application uses the Free Currency API to fetch real-time exchange rate data. The API endpoint is: https://app.freecurrencyapi.com. It returns data in JSON format.

Error Handling
The application implements appropriate error handling for API requests. If there is an issue with fetching the exchange rates, an error message will be displayed to the user.

Contributing
Contributions to this project are welcome. If you have any improvements, bug fixes, or new features to suggest, feel free to open an issue or submit a pull request.

Start the development server:
npm run start in terminal
OR 
Open your web browser and visit http://localhost:3000 to access the application.